trans-unit.source: A collection of <see cref="T:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfo" /> objects.
trans-unit.target: Raccolta di oggetti <see cref="T:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfo" />.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection> object contains <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfo> objects that represent user profiles from a data source.
trans-unit.target: Oggetto <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection> oggetto contiene <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfo> gli oggetti che rappresentano i profili utente da un'origine dati.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection> is returned from the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.GetAllProfiles%2A>, <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.GetAllInactiveProfiles%2A>, <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.FindProfilesByUserName%2A>, and <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.FindInactiveProfilesByUserName%2A> methods of a <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider>.
trans-unit.target: Oggetto <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection> restituito dal <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.GetAllProfiles%2A>, <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.GetAllInactiveProfiles%2A>, <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.FindProfilesByUserName%2A>, e <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.FindInactiveProfilesByUserName%2A> metodi di un <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider>.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection> can be supplied to the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.DeleteProfiles%2A> method to delete profile information and properties from the data source.
trans-unit.target: Oggetto <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection> può essere fornito per il <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.DeleteProfiles%2A> metodo per eliminare le informazioni sul profilo e le proprietà dell'origine dati.

trans-unit.source: The following code example allows a user to search for profiles using the <xref:System.Web.Profile.SqlProfileProvider.FindProfilesByUserName%2A> and <xref:System.Web.Profile.SqlProfileProvider.FindInactiveProfilesByUserName%2A> methods.
trans-unit.target: Esempio di codice seguente consente di cercare profili mediante il <xref:System.Web.Profile.SqlProfileProvider.FindProfilesByUserName%2A> e <xref:System.Web.Profile.SqlProfileProvider.FindInactiveProfilesByUserName%2A> metodi.

trans-unit.source: The user can pass the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection> returned by the `find` methods to the <xref:System.Web.Profile.SqlProfileProvider.DeleteProfiles%2A> method to delete the associated profiles from the data source.
trans-unit.target: L'utente può passare il <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection> restituito dal `find` metodi per il <xref:System.Web.Profile.SqlProfileProvider.DeleteProfiles%2A> metodo per eliminare i profili associati dall'origine dati.

trans-unit.source: Creates a new, empty <see cref="T:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: Crea un nuovo oggetto <see cref="T:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection" /> vuoto.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection> is constructed by profile provider implementers and returned from the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.GetAllProfiles%2A>, <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.GetAllInactiveProfiles%2A>, <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.FindProfilesByUserName%2A>, and <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.FindInactiveProfilesByUserName%2A> methods of the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider> abstract class.
trans-unit.target: Oggetto <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection> viene costruito da implementatori di provider di profili e restituito dal <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.GetAllProfiles%2A>, <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.GetAllInactiveProfiles%2A>, <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.FindProfilesByUserName%2A>, e <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.FindInactiveProfilesByUserName%2A> metodi del <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider> classe astratta.

trans-unit.source: For an example of a <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider> implementation that creates a <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection> for user profiles in a data store, see [Implementing a Profile Provider](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/58de6e99-31a7-41b9-93ed-51b9b4a67e98).
trans-unit.target: Per un esempio di un <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider> implementazione che crea un <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection> per i profili utente in un archivio dati, vedere [implementando un Provider di profilo](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/58de6e99-31a7-41b9-93ed-51b9b4a67e98).

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfo" /> object to add to the collection.
trans-unit.target: Oggetto <see cref="T:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfo" /> da aggiungere all'insieme.

trans-unit.source: Adds the specified <see cref="T:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfo" /> object to the collection.
trans-unit.target: Aggiunge l'oggetto <see cref="T:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfo" /> specificato alla raccolta.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection.Add%2A> method is commonly used by profile-provider implementers to populate a <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection> to return from the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.GetAllProfiles%2A>, <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.GetAllInactiveProfiles%2A>, <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.FindProfilesByUserName%2A>, or <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.FindInactiveProfilesByUserName%2A> method of the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider> abstract class.
trans-unit.target: Il <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection.Add%2A> metodo viene in genere utilizzato per i responsabili dell'implementazione di provider di profili per popolare un <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection> restituisca il <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.GetAllProfiles%2A>, <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.GetAllInactiveProfiles%2A>, <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.FindProfilesByUserName%2A>, o <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.FindInactiveProfilesByUserName%2A> metodo il <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider> classe astratta.

trans-unit.source: For an example of a <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider> implementation that creates a <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection> for user profiles in a data store, see [Implementing a Profile Provider](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/58de6e99-31a7-41b9-93ed-51b9b4a67e98).
trans-unit.target: Per un esempio di un <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider> implementazione che crea un <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection> per i profili utente in un archivio dati, vedere [implementando un Provider di profilo](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/58de6e99-31a7-41b9-93ed-51b9b4a67e98).

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether the profile info collection is thread safe.
trans-unit.target: Ottiene un valore che indica se l'insieme delle informazioni sul profilo è thread-safe.

trans-unit.source: Always <see langword="false" />, because thread-safe profile info collections are not supported.
trans-unit.target: Il valore è sempre <see langword="false" />, poiché gli insiemi di informazioni sul profilo thread-safe non sono supportati.

trans-unit.source: The collection is read-only.
trans-unit.target: Raccolta in sola lettura.

trans-unit.source: Makes the contents of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection" /> read-only.
trans-unit.target: Rende di sola lettura il contenuto dell'oggetto <see cref="T:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection.SetReadOnly%2A> method marks the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection> as read-only so that <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfo> objects cannot be added to or removed from the collection.
trans-unit.target: Il <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection.SetReadOnly%2A> metodo contrassegna il <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection> come di sola lettura in modo che <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfo> oggetti non sono aggiunto o rimosso dalla raccolta.

trans-unit.source: After calling the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection.SetReadOnly%2A> method, you cannot change the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection> back to read/write.
trans-unit.target: Dopo la chiamata di <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection.SetReadOnly%2A> (metodo), non è possibile modificare il <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection> alla lettura/scrittura.

trans-unit.source: Gets the synchronization root.
trans-unit.target: Ottiene la radice di sincronizzazione.

trans-unit.source: Always <see langword="this" /> (<see langword="Me" /> in Visual Basic), because synchronization of <see cref="T:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection" /> objects is not supported.
trans-unit.target: Sempre <see langword="this" /> (<see langword="Me" /> in Visual Basic) poiché la sincronizzazione degli oggetti <see cref="T:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection" /> non è supportata.
